	1
ADVENTURE	1
I.	1
A	1
SCANDAL	1
IN	1
BOHEMIA	1
	1
I.	1
	1
To	1
Sherlock	1
Holmes	1
she	1
is	1
always	1
THE	1
woman.	1
I	1
have	1
seldom	1
heard	1
him	1
mention	1
her	1
under	1
any	1
other	1
name.	1
In	1
his	1
eyes	1
she	1
eclipses	1
and	1
predominates	1
the	1
whole	1
of	1
her	1
sex.	1
It	1
was	1
not	1
that	1
he	1
felt	1
any	1
emotion	1
akin	1
to	1
love	1
for	1
Irene	1
Adler.	1
All	1
emotions,	1
and	1
that	1
one	1
particularly,	1
were	1
abhorrent	1
to	1
his	1
cold,	1
precise	1
but	1
admirably	1
balanced	1
mind.	1
He	1
was,	1
I	1
take	1
it,	1
the	1
most	1
perfect	1
reasoning	1
and	1
observing	1
machine	1
that	1
the	1
world	1
has	1
seen,	1
but	1
as	1
a	1
lover	1
he	1
would	1
have	1
placed	1
himself	1
in	1
a	1
false	1
position.	1
He	1
never	1
spoke	1
of	1
the	1
softer	1
passions,	1
save	1
with	1
a	1
gibe	1
and	1
a	1
sneer.	1
They	1
were	1
admirable	1
things	1
for	1
the	1
observer--excellent	1
for	1
drawing	1
the	1
veil	1
from	1
men's	1
motives	1
and	1
actions.	1
But	1
for	1
the	1
trained	1
reasoner	1
to	1
admit	1
such	1
intrusions	1
into	1
his	1
own	1
delicate	1
and	1
finely	1
adjusted	1
temperament	1
was	1
to	1
introduce	1
a	1
distracting	1
factor	1
which	1
might	1
throw	1
a	1
doubt	1
upon	1
all	1
his	1
mental	1
results.	1
Grit	1
in	1
a	1
sensitive	1
instrument,	1
or	1
a	1
crack	1
in	1
one	1
of	1
his	1
own	1
high-power	1
lenses,	1
would	1
not	1
be	1
more	1
disturbing	1
than	1
a	1
strong	1
emotion	1
in	1
a	1
nature	1
such	1
as	1
his.	1
And	1
yet	1
there	1
was	1
but	1
one	1
woman	1
to	1
him,	1
and	1
that	1
woman	1
was	1
the	1
late	1
Irene	1
Adler,	1
of	1
dubious	1
and	1
questionable	1
memory.	1
	1
I	1
had	1
seen	1
little	1
of	1
Holmes	1
lately.	1
My	1
marriage	1
had	1
drifted	1
us	1
away	1
from	1
each	1
other.	1
My	1
own	1
complete	1
happiness,	1
and	1
the	1
home-centred	1
interests	1
which	1
rise	1
up	1
around	1
the	1
man	1
who	1
first	1
finds	1
himself	1
master	1
of	1
his	1
own	1
establishment,	1
were	1
sufficient	1
to	1
absorb	1
all	1
my	1
attention,	1
while	1
Holmes,	1
who	1
loathed	1
every	1
form	1
of	1
society	1
with	1
his	1
whole	1
Bohemian	1
soul,	1
remained	1
in	1
our	1
lodgings	1
in	1
Baker	1
Street,	1
buried	1
among	1
