	1
The	1
Project	1
Gutenberg	1
Literary	1
Archive	1
Foundation	1
is	1
a	1
non	1
profit	1
501(c)(3)	1
educational	1
corporation	1
organized	1
under	1
the	1
laws	1
of	1
the	1
state	1
of	1
Mississippi	1
and	1
granted	1
tax	1
exempt	1
status	1
by	1
the	1
Internal	1
Revenue	1
Service.	1
	1
The	1
Foundation's	1
EIN	1
or	1
federal	1
tax	1
identification	1
number	1
is	1
64-6221541.	1
	1
Its	1
501(c)(3)	1
letter	1
is	1
posted	1
at	1
http://pglaf.org/fundraising.	1
	1
Contributions	1
to	1
the	1
Project	1
Gutenberg	1
Literary	1
Archive	1
Foundation	1
are	1
tax	1
deductible	1
to	1
the	1
full	1
extent	1
permitted	1
by	1
U.S.	1
federal	1
laws	1
and	1
your	1
state's	1
laws.	1
	1
