Foundation's	1
principal	1
office	1
is	1
located	1
at	1
4557	1
Melan	1
Dr.	1
S.	1
Fairbanks,	1
AK,	1
99712.,	1
but	1
its	1
volunteers	1
and	1
employees	1
are	1
scattered	1
throughout	1
numerous	1
locations.	1
	1
